high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter next to the microwave in the corner.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the sink on the other side of the room.
Place the spoon in the bowl to the right of the loaf of bread.
Pick up the bowl with a spoon in it.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon in it inside the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right to walk around the table, then turn to the left to face the counter with the spatula and spoon.
Pick up the spoon on the counter next to the microwave.
Turn to the left and walk back around the table to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the spoon in the bowl on the counter, which is next to the bread.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon in it.
Walk to the sink.
Put the bowl and spoon into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon in it into the sink.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Move to the counter behind you to the right of the sink.
Place the spoon in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Move to the sink to the left of you.
Place the bowl inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon inside the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the opposite corner of the room and face the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room and face the counter with the tomato on it.
Put the ladle in the bowl in the corner of the counter.
Pick up the bowl with the ladle in it.
Take a step to the left and face the sink.
Put the bowl with ladle in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a bowl with a ladle in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the spoon to the left of the microwave in the corner.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the spoon in the glass bowl on the counter.
Pick up the glass bowl on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass bowl with a spoon in it in the sink.
